lead_paragraph: Japanese teen Nasa Hataoka and two-time European Solheim Cup player Mel Reid shared the second-round lead Thursday in the LPGA Tour qualifying tournament.

headline.print_headline: Japanese Teen Nasa Hataoka, Mel Reid Top LPGA Tour Q-School
